Package edu.rit.image.png

Package edu.rit.image.png contains classes for creating PNG image files.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ChunkOutput
    Interface ChunkOutput specifies the interface for an object to which PNG image file chunks can be written.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    acTLChunk
    Class acTLChunk provides an animation control chunk stored in an APNG file.
    Chunk
    Class Chunk is the abstract base class for a chunk stored in a PNG file.
    ChunkOutputStream
    Class ChunkOutputStream provides an object for writing PNG image chunks to an OutputStream.
    Compressor
    Class Compressor is the abstract base class for an object that compresses a sequence of bytes into PNG chunks and writes the chunks to a ChunkOutput object.
    fcTLChunk
    Class fcTLChunk provides a frame control chunk stored in an APNG file.
    fdATChunk
    Class fdATChunk provides a frame data chunk stored in an APNG file.
    fdATCompressor
    Class fdATCompressor provides an object that compresses a sequence of bytes into APNG fdAT chunks and writes the chunks to a ChunkOutput object.
    IDATChunk
    Class IDATChunk provides an image data chunk stored in a PNG file.
    IDATCompressor
    Class IDATCompressor provides an object that compresses a sequence of bytes into PNG IDAT chunks and writes the chunks to a ChunkOutput object.
    IENDChunk
    Class IENDChunk provides an image trailer chunk stored in a PNG file.
    IHDRChunk
    Class IHDRChunk provides an image header chunk stored in a PNG file.
    pHYsChunk
    Class pHYsChunk provides a physical pixel dimensions chunk stored in a PNG file.
    PLTEChunk
    Class PLTEChunk provides a palette chunk stored in a PNG file.

Package edu.rit.image.png Description

Package edu.rit.image.png contains classes for creating PNG image files.
